{"tid":2157461,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"愛奇藝遭美證交會調查","createTime":"2020-08-15T05:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T05:13:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3fe55bae21120a03b9b17522dc8eb1e94618b1c","tid":2157461,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:09:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200815/2MKQAGR3O5DGHELZMDW4V2X3TM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200815%2F2MKQAGR3O5DGHELZMDW4V2X3TM%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8cIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=fa21803b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200815%2F2MKQAGR3O5DGHELZMDW4V2X3TM%2F&h=86404873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200815/2MKQAGR3O5DGHELZMDW4V2X3TM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n愛奇藝遭美證交會調查<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OtyNkAdzx4wsV3zIWUuigheL6l0=/1280x851/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6MVHD46MLFFGTJBIDW7ASWIY7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOtyNkAdzx4wsV3zIWUuigheL6l0%3D%2F1280x851%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6MVHD46MLFFGTJBIDW7ASWIY7E.jpg&h=2519db94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■愛奇藝股價昨曾跌逾一成。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】 美國零售業反彈。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n按沽空機構報告交資料<br />\n<br />\n內地串流影音平台愛奇藝前日公佈今年次季業績，同時發聲明指被美國證券交易委員會（SEC）調查。愛奇藝向SEC提交自2018年1月以來的財務與營運紀錄，並按沽空機構Wolfpack Research今年4月發出報告內容，提交相關資料。<br />\n<br />\n新浪科技網昨日報道，愛奇藝財務總監王曉東在分析師電話會議指，Wolfpack Research向愛奇藝發表沽空報告數周後，集團收到納指斯克交易所和SEC的調查通知。SEC對愛奇藝的內部審查行動超過四個月，暫無法估計調查結束日期及結果。愛奇藝亦僱用獨立顧問徹查Wolfpack Research報告提出指控。王曉東續指，集團主動披露SEC調查，顯示管理層對業務信心不變。<br />\n<br />\n愛奇藝於今年次季收。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n愛奇藝昨曾跌12.4%至。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"b0ef09a5664e5015cc4e0e6f30751445822e5cb5","tid":2157461,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"咪串啦<br />\n中國有自己既國情業績計算法<br />\n外國唔明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}